{"tha-ap71:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap71:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap71:0.3":"Sumanattheraapadana ","tha-ap71:1.1":"“Sumano nama namena, ","tha-ap71:1.2":"malakaro aham tada; ","tha-ap71:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap71:1.4":"lokahutipatiggaham. ","tha-ap71:2.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap71:2.2":"sumanam pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap71:2.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap71:2.4":"sikhino lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap71:3.1":"Imaya pupphapujaya, ","tha-ap71:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap71:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap71:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap71:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap71:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap71:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap71:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap71:5.1":"Chabbisatimhi kappamhi, ","tha-ap71:5.2":"cattarosum mahayasa; ","tha-ap71:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap71:5.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap71:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap71:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap71:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap71:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap71:8.1":"Sumanattherassapadanam navamam. "}